snippet: Fighter jets from a United States-led coalition hit a gathering of leaders of the Islamic State group in northwestern Iraq on Saturday, and Iraqi officials said they believed a number of top militants had been killed.
abstract: Iraqi officials say that United States airstrikes hit gathering of Islamic State group leaders in northwestern Iraq and killed a number of top militants.
lead_paragraph: Fighter jets from a United States-led coalition hit a gathering of leaders of the Islamic State group in northwestern Iraq on Saturday, and Iraqi officials said they believed a number of top militants had been killed.
